Energy Use

library(ggplot2)
suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(dplyr))
suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(lubridate))
# load gas data
dat <- read.csv('data/xcel_gas.csv',stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
head(dat)
dat <-dat %>% rename(Date=Last.Read.Date,therms=Gas.Usage..Therms.,avgTemp=Average.Temperature) %>% 
  select(Date,therms,avgTemp) %>% 
  mutate(Date=mdy(Date)) %>% 
  mutate(avgTemp=as.integer(gsub("[^0-9]", "", avgTemp) ))
p1 <- dat %>% ggplot(aes(Date,avgTemp))+
    geom_line()+
  geom_point()
p2 <-dat %>% ggplot(aes(Date,therms))+
  geom_line()+
  geom_point()
gridExtra::grid.arrange(p1,p2)

dat %>% ggplot(aes(avgTemp,therms))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method='lm')

dat %>% filter(avgTemp<70) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(avgTemp,therms))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method='lm')

Electric data

dat_ele <- read.csv('data/xcel_electric.csv',stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
head(dat_ele)
dat_ele <-dat_ele %>% rename(Date=Last.Read.Date,kWh=Electric.Usage..kWh.,avgTemp=Average.Temperature) %>% 
  select(Date,kWh,avgTemp) %>% 
  mutate(Date=mdy(Date)) %>% 
  mutate(avgTemp=as.integer(gsub("[^0-9]", "", avgTemp) ))
head(dat_ele)
dat_ele %>% ggplot(aes(Date,kWh))+
  geom_point()

dat_ele %>% ggplot(aes(avgTemp,kWh))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method = 'lm')
